Type: ShinyApp
Title: AI SQL Chatbot
Version: 0.2.0
Description: A Shiny app for natural language to SQL data analysis, powered
    by Claude (Anthropic) via the ellmer package. Ask questions about your
    data in plain English and get SQL queries, results, and summaries.
    Supports SQLite, DuckDB (for tibbles/dataframes), and remote databases
    via ADBC (Arrow Database Connectivity).
Authors@R: person("Javier", "Orraca-Deatcu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Imports:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    shinychat,
    ellmer,
    DBI,
    RSQLite,
    reactable,
    htmltools,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    duckdb,
    adbi,
    adbcdrivermanager
